author: WCAX News
title: NY State Police on lookout for missing teen
text:
CLINTON COUNTY, N.Y. - This morning authorities are searching for a Clinton County teen who went missing last night.
Police say 14-year-old Chris Jerdo was last seen wearing a blue Hollister shirt, blue jeans and a green and yellow flat brimmed hat. He was last seen around 9:30 near Ausable Valley Central High School. Anyone with information is asked to contact New York State Police.
